2000-1666 (La. 10/14/02)

STATE ex rel. Joseph ZINA, Jr. v. STATE of Louisiana. No. 2000-KH-1666. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 14, 2002.

In re Joseph Zina, Jr.-Defendant; Applying for Motion to Enforce Order of this Court dated August 23, 2000; Parish of Orleans Criminal District Court Div. E., No. 282-576.

Denied. Moot. The district court has acted.
